<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 22:05:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>杀害底特律犹太教堂主席萨曼莎·沃尔的嫌疑人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/suspect-arrested-in-killing-of-detroit-synagogue-president-samantha-woll/0000018b-b0a6-df42-a78f-bde765470000</link><description>40 岁的萨曼莎·沃尔 (Samantha Woll) 上个月被发现死在家外。周三，底特律警方宣布逮捕一名嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 20:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/suspect-arrested-in-killing-of-detroit-synagogue-president-samantha-woll/0000018b-b0a6-df42-a78f-bde765470000</guid></item><item><title>英国的犹太学生在一个月内面临“一年多的反犹太事件”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/jewish-students-in-the-u-k-face-over-a-years-worth-of-antisemitic-incidents-in-a-month/0000018b-aff0-dedf-adab-eff04f440000</link><description>该组织表示，面对辱骂、恐吓和死亡威胁，犹太学生已向犹太学生联盟的福利热线拨打了 400 多个电话</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 19:37:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/jewish-students-in-the-u-k-face-over-a-years-worth-of-antisemitic-incidents-in-a-month/0000018b-aff0-dedf-adab-eff04f440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的 TROPHY 系统如何在加沙保护坦克免受反坦克火力攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-trophy-system-protects-tanks-from-anti-tank-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</link><description>在哈马斯的视频中，以色列坦克被反坦克火箭击中，但在许多情况下，它们实际上表明旨在拦截威胁的技术正在发挥作用</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 19:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-trophy-system-protects-tanks-from-anti-tank-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-af67-dedf-adab-ef779df60000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不应该上映展示哈马斯暴行的电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-08/ty-article/.highlight/why-israel-shouldnt-release-the-film-showing-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-b019-d3c1-a39b-bef9b4930000</link><description>哈马斯大屠杀的视觉证据并不缺乏。但有无数的历史、政治和心理原因让人们观看它并看到与以色列人期望的完全不同的东西</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 19:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-08/ty-article/.highlight/why-israel-shouldnt-release-the-film-showing-hamas-atrocities/0000018b-b019-d3c1-a39b-bef9b4930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方收集哈马斯袭击期间轮奸的目击者证词</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/israeli-police-collect-eyewitness-testimony-of-gang-rape-during-hamas-attack/0000018b-b025-d3c1-a39b-bee5ef400000</link><description>警方调查人员一直在收集哈马斯恐怖分子在 10 月 7 日袭击期间实施性侵犯和性虐待行为的目击者的证词。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/israeli-police-collect-eyewitness-testimony-of-gang-rape-during-hamas-attack/0000018b-b025-d3c1-a39b-bee5ef400000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击一周年之际，家人讲述了痛苦、失落和对政府的愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/marking-one-month-to-hamas-attack-families-speak-of-pain-loss-and-anger-at-government/0000018b-afbc-d3c1-a39b-bffdb5240000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列为遇难者举行哀悼日，遇难者家属聚集在特拉维夫悼念亲​​人。其中一位承诺：那些对这场灾难负责的人“将回家、入狱或下地狱”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:32:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/marking-one-month-to-hamas-attack-families-speak-of-pain-loss-and-anger-at-government/0000018b-afbc-d3c1-a39b-bffdb5240000</guid></item><item><title>帮助经历 10 月 7 日袭击事件、遭受创伤的以色列儿童再次成为孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/helping-traumatized-israeli-children-who-experienced-the-october-7-attack-be-kids-again/0000018b-afe7-dea2-a9bf-ffffdfe70000</link><description>以色列救生联合会的成员每周都会举办几次游戏，帮助孩子们重建恢复能力。创始人保罗·哈基姆 (Paul Hakim) 解释说：“我们让大脑告诉身体一切都好。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/helping-traumatized-israeli-children-who-experienced-the-october-7-attack-be-kids-again/0000018b-afe7-dea2-a9bf-ffffdfe70000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争爆发一个月后，以色列正在经历一个超越政治的时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/one-month-into-gaza-war-israel-is-experiencing-a-moment-that-transcends-politics/0000018b-afbe-d3c1-a39b-bfff853a0000</link><description>极端正统派男子正在为军队签名，阿拉伯以色列人正在与犹太以色列人一起帮助流离失所者。但不要过于乐观——自 10 月 7 日以来，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和他的顽固支持者并没有改变</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 17:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/one-month-into-gaza-war-israel-is-experiencing-a-moment-that-transcends-politics/0000018b-afbe-d3c1-a39b-bfff853a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府将接受私人捐款资助加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-will-accept-private-donations-to-fund-war-in-gaza/0000018b-af50-dea2-a9bf-ffde12340000</link><description>批评者表示，该指令为外部对政府优先事项的不当影响和对普通公民的剥削打开了大门</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-will-accept-private-donations-to-fund-war-in-gaza/0000018b-af50-dea2-a9bf-ffde12340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列扣留资金帮助战争撤离人员的真正原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/the-real-reason-israel-is-holding-up-money-to-help-war-evacuees/0000018b-af8d-df42-a78f-afcfabe10000</link><description>没有钱请正统派老师吗？那么以色列战争撤离者也没有钱：以色列政府试图淡化这个等式</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:25:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/the-real-reason-israel-is-holding-up-money-to-help-war-evacuees/0000018b-af8d-df42-a78f-afcfabe10000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔的认罪笔录在他发动的战争中重新审视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-confession-transcript-reexamined-amid-a-war-he-started/0000018b-af64-dea2-a9bf-fffe1c080000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙对哈马斯发动战争，有关哈马斯领导人和 10 月 7 日建筑师叶海亚·辛瓦尔 (Yahya Sinwar) 的记忆被重新唤起，他曾因谋杀罪在以色列服无期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-confession-transcript-reexamined-amid-a-war-he-started/0000018b-af64-dea2-a9bf-fffe1c080000</guid></item><item><title>“即使在伦敦也很可怕”：六名以色列人逃离该国开始新生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-here-in-london-its-scary-what-being-an-israeli-abroad-now-is-like/0000018b-ae87-df42-a78f-afc7cf810000</link><description>奥里特（Orit）是一位导乐师，虽然身在佐治亚州，但仍在帮助她的老客户生孩子；安德烈（Andrey）对他所看到的视频感到震惊；亚登（Yarden）正在勇敢地面对伦敦喧闹的抗议活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-here-in-london-its-scary-what-being-an-israeli-abroad-now-is-like/0000018b-ae87-df42-a78f-afc7cf810000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的内塔尼亚胡仍然向普京和俄罗斯卑躬屈膝？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-is-israels-netanyahu-still-groveling-to-putin-and-russia/0000018b-af21-dea2-a9bf-ffbf3e0c0000</link><description>十年来，以色列一直急于安抚莫斯科。但内塔尼亚胡坦率地对莫斯科采取令人尴尬的绥靖政策并没有带来明显的收获。相反，在 10 月 7 日的暴行发生后，普京立即加强了与伊朗的合作并接待了哈马斯领导人</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-is-israels-netanyahu-still-groveling-to-putin-and-russia/0000018b-af21-dea2-a9bf-ffbf3e0c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列模特被选为迪奥广告大片后，亲巴勒斯坦活动人士呼吁抵制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-activists-call-for-boycott-after-israeli-model-is-chosen-for-dior-campaign/0000018b-af36-dea2-a9bf-ffbe3be30000</link><description>这家著名的法国时装公司邀请以色列人 May Tager 参与圣诞广告活动，引发了社交媒体上大量愤怒的帖子。 “迪奥选择凶手是为了他们的竞选活动，现在一切都散发着血腥味”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:01:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-activists-call-for-boycott-after-israeli-model-is-chosen-for-dior-campaign/0000018b-af36-dea2-a9bf-ffbe3be30000</guid></item><item><title>共和党总统候选人在迈阿密辩论中激烈交锋，巴勒斯坦人、反犹太主义成为首要议程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-top-hit-list-as-gop-candidates-minus-trump-lock-horns-in-miami-debate/0000018b-af10-d3c1-a39b-bff18cde0000</link><description>尽管前总统唐纳德·特朗普缺席了周三由共和党犹太联盟共同发起的电视辩论，但随着候选人讨论以色列-加沙战争和国内反犹太主义抬头，他的影响力将不容忽视</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 14:50:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-top-hit-list-as-gop-candidates-minus-trump-lock-horns-in-miami-debate/0000018b-af10-d3c1-a39b-bff18cde0000</guid></item><item><title>5万名加沙人在停火、释放人质谈判中向南迁移；摩萨德挫败真主党在巴西的阴谋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-live/soldier-killed-in-gaza-biden-confirms-asking-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pause/0000018b-ad28-d0f8-a39b-fd3a1c820000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的两名士兵的姓名 ■ 布林肯首先明确呼吁巴勒斯坦领导的治理，并在巴勒斯坦权力机构的支持下加沙与西岸统一 ■ 加兰特表示，战后以色列将在加沙享有充分的行动自由 ■由于需要资助战争，以色列总检察长下令冻结联军资金 ■ 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀中至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵死亡，241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：超过 10,000 人被杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 14:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-live/soldier-killed-in-gaza-biden-confirms-asking-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pause/0000018b-ad28-d0f8-a39b-fd3a1c820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列厨师埃亚尔·沙尼 (Eyal Shani) 在为以色列国防军士兵煎牛排时荣获首颗米其林星</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/while-flipping-steaks-for-idf-soldiers-israeli-chef-eyal-shani-gets-first-michelin-star/0000018b-af1e-d3c1-a39b-bfff8fdc0000</link><description>这位著名的以色列餐厅老板以其纽约餐厅“Shmona”赢得了顶级烹饪皇冠上的宝石。沙尼 (Shani) 成为第四位获得米其林星的以色列厨师</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 13:57:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/while-flipping-steaks-for-idf-soldiers-israeli-chef-eyal-shani-gets-first-michelin-star/0000018b-af1e-d3c1-a39b-bfff8fdc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争，冲突已持续一个月。什么样的未来？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-with-hamas-one-month-into-the-conflict-what-lies-ahead/0000018b-aeaa-d3c1-a39b-beeb5d510000</link><description>《国土报》和加州大学洛杉矶分校举办了一场视频讨论，讨论以色列潜在的退出战略、政治后果和公众在加沙战争中的沮丧情绪：“我们正走向政治动荡最激烈的时期之一”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 13:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-with-hamas-one-month-into-the-conflict-what-lies-ahead/0000018b-aeaa-d3c1-a39b-beeb5d510000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家可能在加利利海发现了耶稣使徒的传统家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-site-early-christians-venerated-as-apostle-peters-home/0000018b-ae8c-d3c1-a39b-beedd7520000</link><description>在他们认为是伯赛大的村庄里一座早期教堂的下面，考古学家发现了一堵“圣墙”——这不可能是来自使徒彼得的房子。然而，旁边的那个可能是</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 13:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-site-early-christians-venerated-as-apostle-peters-home/0000018b-ae8c-d3c1-a39b-beedd7520000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗核事务负责人：部长威胁“用核武器攻击加沙”证实了以色列的能力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/iran-nuclear-chief-ministers-threat-to-nuke-gaza-confirms-israels-capability/0000018b-aecb-df42-a78f-afcbcbcd0000</link><description>伊朗的穆罕默德·伊斯拉米表示，“犹太复国主义政权已经承认拥有核武器，更重要的是，威胁着加沙受压迫的无辜人民”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 12:35:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/iran-nuclear-chief-ministers-threat-to-nuke-gaza-confirms-israels-capability/0000018b-aecb-df42-a78f-afcbcbcd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>